{"tid":2414544,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"HK01吹風 : 假安心出行或觸犯「版權條例」、偽造或詐騙等罪行，若市民使用或涉「使用虛假文書」!","createTime":"2021-02-19T13:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T14:33:19.000Z","uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4558a5a18a338b4fb4fea19250649e3c98cb019f","tid":2414544,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:06:31.000Z","msg":"政府於周四（18日）起放寬防疫禁令，晚市堂食、健身室等處所重開，但市民必須掃瞄「安心出行」二維碼，或登記個人資料。不過，表明罷用「安心出行」，更有人設計「翻版安心出行」，抄襲正版設計。<br />\n<br />\n有律師指出，「翻版安心出行」的設計者有機會觸犯《版權條例》、偽造或詐騙等罪行；若市民使用，或涉「使用虛假文書」等罪。資訊科技專家指出，設計翻版並不復雜，所用的是軟件開發常用的平台「GitLab」，執法機構要追查開發者及使用者，技術上可行。"},{"pid":"f39a36c033fe158497ae334efd3d2378d7b07a66","tid":2414544,"uid":2054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:11:00.000Z","msg":"為咗偷資料有權用到盡"},{"pid":"35fd1309c7e3c918affd7cdc66d090a96eabfc70","tid":2414544,"uid":151534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:14:08.000Z","msg":"封一個GitLab,仲有千千萬萬個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e128d909a4a3a9818e64fa8a711ebef5494ed3","tid":2414544,"uid":35429,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"35fd1309c7e3c918affd7cdc66d090a96eabfc70","tid":2414544,"uid":151534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:14:08.000Z","msg":"封一個GitLab,仲有千千萬萬個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:16:57.000Z","msg":"封咗github gitlab 佢囉，依兩個網支那都唔敢封，因為封咗IT狗會暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142abd0afabdcb0528dab27f76b9c117300e9999","tid":2414544,"uid":151534,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a1e128d909a4a3a9818e64fa8a711ebef5494ed3","tid":2414544,"uid":35429,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"35fd1309c7e3c918affd7cdc66d090a96eabfc70","tid":2414544,"uid":151534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:14:08.000Z","msg":"封一個GitLab,仲有千千萬萬個<img s